c: 60
v: 12
t: "Eehey ma annabi si rew…ìe juul…ìe ngari e ma ho…ìe coodandira e ma nde …ìe ndenndintah Alla e hay gooto,ngujjatah, njinatah, mbaratah sukaa…ìe mum en,ngaddatah fenaande fepindaande hakkunde juu…óe mum en e koy…óe mum en,…ìe ngoopataa Ma e mo∆¥∆¥ere ndeen de soodandir e mum en, yaafnano…ìe Alla, pellet Alla ko jaafatoo…óo jurmotoo…óo"